WEBSITE USE





     Your access to NRG SERVICES’ Website(s)
is conditional upon and limited by the terms of this Website Access Agreement
as follows.  When you visit or use our
sites, you agree to be bound by the terms and conditions set forth herein or
incorporated herein by reference.  NRG SERVICES reserves the right to amend or modify the terms hereof at any time in
its sole discretion.  If and when we
amend or modify these provisions, we will notify you by posting the amended or
modified terms on this website. 
Amendments and modifications are effective upon such posting.


     1.   
						Service and Product Information.


     NRG SERVICES attempts to use its best
reasonable efforts to provide information about its services and products that
is up to date and accurate, but we do not warrant such information to be
so.  Pricing errors may be corrected by
NRG SERVICES at any time any way up to and including canceling your order.  We would appreciate you notifying us if you
see an error.


     2.   
						Warranty Disclaimer.


     NRG SERVICES disclaims all warranties,
express or implied, including without limitation implied warranties of
merchantability and/or fitness for a particular purpose as to the information,
content, services and products on our website. 
We do not warrant the site information to be error free or up to date or
that downloads from the site will be free of viruses, worms, Trojan horses or
other destructive codes.  Nor do we
warrant or represent that our website or servers are immune from hacking or
other unauthorized access or that your access and use of the site will be
uninterrupted, free of errors, or otherwise meet your requirements.


     3.   
						Limitation of Liability.


     In no event shall NRG SERVICES be liable
for any direct, indirect, special or consequential damages or any other damages
of any kind, including but not limited to loss of use, loss of profits, or loss
of data, whether in an action in contract warranty, tort, including but not
limited to negligence or otherwise, arising out of or in any way connected with
(a) the use or inability to use our Website(s) or the content, materials,
information or transactions provided on or through the sites, or (b) any claim
attributable to errors, omissions, or other inaccuracies in the sites or the
content, materials, information, products, or services on or available through
the sites, even if NRG SERVICES or its authorized agents have been advised of
the possibility of such damages.


     In no event shall the aggregate liability
of NRG SERVICES whether in contract, warranty, tort, including negligence
whether active, passive, or imputed, product liability, strict liability, or any
other theory, arising out of or relating to the use of NRG SERVICES’ sites,
exceed $10.00 or the amount you paid NRG SERVICES, whichever is less.  


     In states that do not allow limitations on
damages or implied warranties, NRG SERVICES’ liability is limited to the
greatest extent permitted by such state’s law.


     4.   
						Change of Site Content.


     NRG SERVICES reserves the right to
change, including delete, any and all content contained on our websites at any
time without notice.  Reference to any
product, service or other information, by manufacturer, trade-name, supplier or
otherwise does not constitute or imply our endorsement or recommendation
thereof.


