format, design, text, photos, graphics, sound files and other files are ALL
RIGHTS RESERVED copyright © 2010 NRG SERVICES, LLC.  By this limited license, you may personally
access the websites and print materials only for your personal and
non-commercial use.  No other use of our
websites is granted to you nor are you granted any other right or license,
express or implicit or otherwise, to use our sites.  Unauthorized use of our websites terminates
the limited license allowing you access to our websites and may violate
applicable laws governing copyrights and communications.





     6.   
						Username/Password.


     In order to access some areas of our
websites you will need a username and password. 
As with all usernames and passwords, you are responsible for protecting
the confidentiality of yours and you are responsible for all transactions and
other actions that take place under your username and password.  If you believe the confidentially of either
or both your username and password have been compromised, you must notify us as
soon as possible so that we may take remedial action that we believe in our
sole discretion to be necessary.  We will
never be liable to you for any damage or injury arising or resulting from our
actions or omissions under this provision or from any confidentiality breach or
unauthorized access of your password or account.


