About the Company
Online Services
Products
Reviews


NRG Home Warranty & Maintenance offers you products that are designed to protect your home against unexpected repair costs. The company claims that they go beyond what other companies offer and provide premium coverage plans which would even enhance the value of a home.

The company currently offers services in Dallas and Houston, Texas. NRG Home Services believe that they are competitive and that their plans are priced reasonably. The company is headquartered in Houston, Texas and offers a host of services ranging from AC checkups, plumbing issues to electrical maintenance needs. 


NRG has a host of maintenance and warranty services to offer their customers. The company claim that they are dependable and are always trying to come up with ways to ensure that customer satisfaction is maintained. They also have a 24/7 claims system which customers can connect with should they require any service. They also have a very effective pest control service made available to their members.

The company maintains a well managed website which can meet almost all the online needs of their customers. Plans can be purchased and kept track of through this website which is also equipped to take in online claims. All these factors combined together, NRG Home Services seems like a company that the Texans would love.


Products and services offered by NRG include the following 5 categories
Home ServicesAC & HeatingElectricalPest ControlPlumbingTo handle these problems, NRG has a large network of licensed, skilled technicians who are dispatched as and when a customer reports a problem.

Apart from the above described maintenance services, NRG also offers comprehensive home warranty plans to both homeowners and Realtors. The company claims that unlike a few other home warranty companies, their home warranty plans provide a no-fault coverage which means that coverage begins the moment you purchase it.

A standard home warranty plan from NRG costs approximately $395 per year and the deductible applicable for this plan is $65.

 
















