Jocelyn Durant - TX  - 2017-06-01



2017-06-01
										
										I have had Landmark since April. I have since had to use them twice, the first to have the house rekeyed and had the most amazing service from Landmark and the service provider. The second service request for was the dishwasher which stopped working which we discovered after closing. Landmark provided excellent customer service throughout this process with prompt follow up, efforts to find and locate parts and contacting the service provider when needed. They were able to solve my challenge with a pay out. I have been extremely satisfied with Landmark Warranty and would highly recommend them to others!
									



Heather - TX  - 2017-05-31



2017-05-31
										
										This is the second home we have warrantied thru Landmark. Our experiences have always been positive. Most of our claims have been appliance repairs (fridge and washing machine). 
Some of the contractors have been better than others but all seemed adequate and several were outstanding. If there have been delays in repairs it is typically because a part had to be ordered or because the issue occurred on the weekend when contractor was not working. You cannot fault the warranty company or even contractor for that! My thought is that if I\'m able to get what would otherwise be an expensive out of pocket repair completed for a minimal charge and a few days wait then I\'m getting what I paid for. I have been pleased with the polite and helpful staff at Landmark when I\'ve placed calls about a service request. If everything continues as it has thus far, I expect to continue doing business with Landmark for years to come. 
									















